title: OnePlus 10 Ultra to reportedly pack improved cameras and Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 Plus
content:
OnePlus recently expanded its 2022 number series with the launch of the OnePlus 10R. It joins the OnePlus 10 Pro, the best smartphone that OnePlus currently has to offer.
